channel.title: Is there any easy to setup Runescape 500-700ish server software?
channel.description:
My development team has been working hard these past 3 days to create a vanilla Runescape 2 private server for conventional use, but we can't seem to find any good software for 500-700ish any were. Could I possibly get a site to a 500-700ish server software? If anyone knows how to work one and easily help please add my Skype, "Zachary.furgeson". I'd greatly appreciate the support. We attempted with a server software by the name of "Joltv2".
Also, I apologize if this is in the wrong area as I couldn't find a request topic.
Again, my Skype is, "Zachary.furgeson".
